    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Shades with narrow, sharply pleated folds, resembling the musical instrument. For shades that pull up in wide horizontal pleats, use "Roman shades."</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000099620/Legacy AAT data</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Persianas con dobleces plisados, agudos y delgados, que se parecen al instrumento musical. Para formas que se tiran hacia arriba en amplios pliegues horizontales, use "persiana romana”.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Spanish</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000131/CDBP-SNPC</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000051034/TAA database (2000-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Gordijnen met smalle, scherp gevouwen plooien die op het muziekinstrument, de accordeon, lijken. Gebruik vouwgordijnen voor gordijnen die in brede, horizontale plooien omhoog worden getrokken.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000205/AAT-Ned</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000113770/AAT-Ned (1994-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>此種簾幕具有類似手風琴的窄摺片。若指具有可上拉的橫向寬摺片的簾幕，則稱為「羅曼簾」。</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Chinese (traditional)</Note_Language>
